  <ethicsAndSummary>
    <summary>40 patients who are to undergo total hip replacement (THR) will be randomly allocated to either Anterior or Lateral Groups. Otherwise identical THR operations will be performed.
Xrays will be assessed for component positioning.
Patients will fill out a self assessment form at Preop, and Postop 6 weeks, 3, 6, and 12 months
(Harris Hip Score )
Objective data collection will include blood loss, length of Hospital stay, and time on crutches.</summary>
